 # 抛物线及直线的回归计算[游戏中弹道预测算法核心].js
```
/**
 * 最小二乘法拟合抛物线，算法参考 https://blog.csdn.net/shenziheng1/article/details/54409527
 * @param {array} originalData [[x1,y1],[x2,y2], ]
 * @returns {array} [交点1，交点2，[A,B,C]]
 */
function unLinearAndFindIntersection(originalData) {
    var sum_x1 = 0, sum_x2 = 0, sum_x3 = 0, sum_x4 = 0, sum_y1 = 0, sum_y1x1 = 0, sum_y1x2 = 0;
    var n = originalData.length;
    for (let i = 0; i < n; i++) {
        var x1 = originalData[i][0][0];
        var x2 = x1 * x1;
        var x3 = x2 * x1;
        var x4 = x3 * x1;
        var y1 = originalData[i][0][1];
        sum_x1 += x1;
        sum_x2 += x2;
        sum_x3 += x3;
        sum_x4 += x4;
        sum_y1 += y1;
        sum_y1x1 += y1 * x1;
        sum_y1x2 += y1 * x2;
    }
    //解三元一次方程，输入方程组a*x + b*y + c*z = d各系数，输出Ax^2 + By + C = 0各系数
    var a = sum_x4, e = sum_x3, i = sum_x2,
        b = sum_x3, f = sum_x2, j = sum_x1,
        c = sum_x2, g = sum_x1, k = n,
        d = sum_y1x2, h = sum_y1x1, l = sum_y1;
    var valueD = a * f * k + b * g * i + c * e * j - c * f * i - a * g * j - b * e * k;
    var valueX = d * f * k + b * g * l + c * h * j - c * f * l - d * g * j - b * h * k;
    var valueY = a * h * k + d * g * i + c * e * l - c * h * i - d * e * k - a * g * l;
    var valueZ = a * f * l + b * h * i + d * e * j - d * f * i - b * e * l - a * h * j;
    var A = valueX / valueD;
    var B = valueY / valueD;
    var C = valueZ / valueD;
    //求根公式解出(与x轴)交点
    var delta = Math.sqrt(Math.pow(B, 2) - 4 * A * C);
    if (delta < 0) {
        return [null, null, [A, B, C]];
    } else if (delta == 0) {
        var resultA = (-B + delta) / (2 * A);
        return [resultA, resultA, [A, B, C]];
    } else {
        var resultA = (-B + delta) / (2 * A);
        var resultB = (-B - delta) / (2 * A);
        return [resultA, resultB, [A, B, C]];
    }

}
/**
 * 最小二乘法拟合直线
 * @param {Array} data [[x,y],[x,y], ]
 * @returns {Array} 
 */
function linearRegression(data) {
    //y=Ax+B
    var sum_x1 = 0, sum_y1 = 0, valueA = 0, valueB = 0;
    var n = data.length;
    for (let i = 0; i < n; i++) {
        var x1 = data[i][1][0];
        var y1 = data[i][1][1];
        sum_x1 += x1;
        sum_y1 += y1;
    }
    var average_x1 = sum_x1 / n;
    var average_y1 = sum_y1 / n;
    for (let i = 0; i < n; i++) {
        var x1 = data[i][1][0];
        var y1 = data[i][1][1];
        valueA += ((y1 - average_y1) * (x1 - average_x1));
        valueB += Math.pow(x1 - average_x1, 2);
    }
    var A = valueA / valueB;
    var B = average_y1 - A * average_x1;
    return [A, B];
}
